<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَضِقِ الوَقْتُ؛ فَتَجِبُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(وَإِذَا نَابَهُ)</span> أَيْ عَرَضَ لِمُصَلٍّ <span class="c2">(شَيْءٌ)</span> أَيْ أَمْرٌ؛ كَاسْتِئْذَانِ إِنْسَانٍ عَلَيْهِ،<span class="c5"> وَسَهْوِ إِمَامِهِ:</span> <span class="c2">(سَبَّحَ)</span> بِإِمَامٍ وُجُوبًا، وَمُسْتَأْذِنٍ اسْتِحْبَابًا <span class="c2">(رَجُلٌ)</span>، وَلَا تَبْطُلُ إِنْ كَثُرَ، <span class="c2">(وَصَفَّقَتِ اِمْرَأَةٌ بِبَطْنِ كَفِّهَا عَلَى ظَهْرِ الأُخْرَى)</span>، وَتَبْطُلُ إِنْ كَثُرَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(وَيُزِيلُ)</span> مُصَلٍّ <span class="c2">(بُصَاقًا وَنَحْوَهُ)</span> كَمُخَاطٍ وَنُخَامَةٍ <span class="c2">(بِثَوْبِهِ)</span> إِنْ بَدَرَهُ وَهُوَ فِي الصَّلَاةِ، <span class="c2">(وَيُبَاحُ)</span> بُصَاقٌ وَنَحْوُهُ <span class="c2">(فِي غَيْرِ مَسْجِدٍ عَنْ يَسَارِهِ)</span>، وَتَحْتَ قَدَمِهِ اليُسْرَى، وَفِي ثَوْبِهِ أَوْلَى، <span class="c2">(وَيُكْرَهُ)</span> بَصْقُهُ وَنَحْوُهُ <span class="c2">(أَمَامَهُ وَيَمِينَهُ)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(فَصْلٌ)</span> فِي أَرْكَانِ الصَّلَاةِ وَوَاجِبَاتِهَا وَسُنَنِهَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(وَجُمْلَةُ أَرْكَانِهَا)</span> أَيِ الصَّلَاةِ <span class="c2">(أَرْبَعَةَ عَشَرَ)</span> رُكْنًا:<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">الأَوَّلُ:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقِيَامُ)</span> فِي فَرْضِهَا، مَعَ القُدْرَةِ عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الثَّانِي: <span class="c2">(التَّحْرِيمَةُ)</span> أَيْ قَوْلُ: <span class="c2">«اللهُ أَكْبَرُ»</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الثَّالِثُ: <span class="c2">(الْفَاتِحَةُ)</span> عَلَى غَيْرِ مَأْمُومٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الرَّابِعُ: <span class="c2">(الرُّكُوعُ)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الخَامِسُ: <span class="c2">(الِاعْتِدَالُ عَنْهُ)</span> أَيِ الرُّكُوعِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> السَّادِسُ: <span class="c2">(السُّجُودُ)</span>؛ فِي كُلِّ رَكْعَةٍ مَرَّتَيْنِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> السَّابِعُ: <span class="c2">(الِاعْتِدَالُ عَنْهُ)</span> أَيِ السُّجُودِ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الثَّامِنُ: <span class="c2">(الْجُلُوسُ بَيْنَ السَّجْدَتَيْنِ)</span>.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> التَّاسِعُ: <span class="c2">(الطُّمَأْنِينَةُ)</span>، وَهِيَ السُّكُونُ فِي كُلِّ رُكْنٍ فِعْلِيٍّ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> العَاشِرُ: <span class="c2">(التَّشَهُّدُ الأَخِيرُ)</span>.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c2">(وَ)</span> الحَادِي عَشَرَ: <span class="c2">(جَلْسَتُهُ)</span> أَيِ التَّشَهُّدِ الأَخِيرِ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>